<%- include('../partials/tw-head') -%>
<body class="flex min-h-full flex-col bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 antialiased">
<%- include('../partials/tw-header') -%>
<main class="flex-1">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-navy py-14 text-white sm:py-16">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_88%_0%,rgba(217,119,6,0.2),transparent_45%)]"></div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-200/90">About Faith Based Innovations, LLC</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 max-w-4xl text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">We build with stewardship, discipline, and deep respect for serious work.</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-200">Faith Based Innovations, LLC is a faith-based software company creating premium desktop products with clear boundaries and clear accountability. We build with intent, clarity, and respect for your data and your time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/5">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Faith-based stewardship</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Faith Based Innovations, LLC is rooted in stewardship and disciplined work. We believe software should serve people with honesty, structure, and responsibility rather than manipulation or hype.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/5">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Standalone product missions</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-navy">CFO</strong>, <strong class="text-navy">Eden</strong>, and <strong class="text-navy">Ledger</strong> are each standalone products with distinct jobs. We do not collapse finance, research, and identity into one confusing app.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/5">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Controlled intelligence</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"><%= SITE.steward.name %> is our controlled, rules-based intelligence layer. It is deterministic, auditable, and trustworthy by design—not open-ended generation and not magic.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-y border-slate-200 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center lg:px-8">
      <article>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">Local-first and privacy-first by conviction</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Serious work belongs on serious machines. Faith Based Innovations, LLC rejects cloud dependency and surveillance-style growth models that treat users like telemetry feeds.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Our products are engineered for local-first workflows and privacy-first operation, so control stays with the person doing the work.</p>
      </article>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-inner">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-slate-500">How we build</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-faithGold"></span>Deliberate architecture over rushed feature churn</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-faithGold"></span>Deterministic guidance over probabilistic guesswork</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-faithGold"></span>Clear product boundaries over ambiguous all-in-one UX</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-faithGold"></span>Respect for user data, attention, and long-term trust</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">Built with intent and accountability</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Faith Based Innovations, LLC does not ship noise. We build premium desktop software with clear missions, transparent behavior, and principled engineering so serious users can do serious work with confidence.</p>
  </section>
</main>
<%- include('../partials/tw-footer') %>
<%- include('../partials/tw-scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
